
## Project 2 Connect 4

Cameron Garratt (810-382-829)

## Instructions

To clean my code (i.e., remove any compiled files), type:

```
$ make clean
```

To compile my code, type:

```
$ make compile
```

To run my code (after compiling it), type one of the following:

```
$ make run 
```

##About the game

To play the game, assuming you are human, you will at first be prompted to enter your name.
After doing so, you will be presented a board.
Choose a number 1-7 to enter. Entering a number will place a piece at the location
of your choosing. The objective is to connect 4 pieces in a row. Good luck! 

